reviews.review_text:
under rated show I was able to download this before they shut it down very under rated show crystal sound real strong jerry good vocals and phil is clean and punchy billy sounds at the top of his game there something about him on his own he was dancin the kit just listen from start to end you will not be disapointed enjoy this hidden gem from what i have as the best of the dead in all thier runs you cant match there sound and jerry was just the best during these years his giutar was but jerry giutar sounds a little to soft in this mixi thought black throated was some funky stuff going on toward the end but the come back with a solid scarlet b. great Row Jimmy .donna sounds good no really she does I am not kidding really  ok she sounds ok  but the sound is outstanding 
i wish they would let us download again anyone interested in trading some of the shows just drop me a line

I'm really impressed by this show! For what that's worth... 
The recording (so far) sounds exceptionally clear, but I think its just the band really patient and listening to each other... Don't get me wrong, its not like I don't love those crazed screaming million mile an hour shows... But this is great on a calm Sunday morning, self-isolating during the Pandemic of 2020! Its one of the good take aways! But perhaps, I have actually, finally, lost my mind! And then the vocals dropped out... second set...
